cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.NE, cs.CL 

The paper discusses training regimes for deep learning and proposes a meta-learning algorithm to mitigate catastrophic forgetting. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE), and computational linguistics (cs.CL). However, since the paper focuses on deep learning and sequential learning problems, cs.LG and cs.AI are the most likely sub-categories.
